
Build contexts
--------------

Template:

[platform]_[host]_[toolchain]_[flavour]_[arch]

platform  : API for which a software is written [posix, winnt, amiga, ...]
host      : operating system that provides said API [winnt, linux, ...]
toolchain : compiler suite and tools [gcc, sasc, vcpp, ...]
flavour   : type of build [debug, release, ...]
arch      : processor architecture [x86, amd64, ppc, mips, 68k...]


Examples:

posix_linux_gcc_debug
posix_fbsd
posix_macosx
posix_win2k
winnt_winxp_vcpp_release_amd64
winnt_win2k
macosx_macosx
amiga_aos3_sasc_release
amiga_morphos
amiga_aros_gcc_debug
